des:
At Tymbal, we are dedicated to building tools that help bloggers grow. This skill demonstrates how the Tymbal Reader can read your blog out loud to your readers. 

Make your blog speak. Contact us today to see how we can offer you a custom Alexa Skill and to let your readers listen to your content. 

Go to www.tymbalreader.com to get started today.
